    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/d0bb3e40698d087fce22a96e5df84c25.avif?t=1771272977\" width=600 height=85 /></span>暴君登陆泰伯利亚，承诺把这里打造为天堂，没有战争，没有苦难……也没有死亡。要进入暴君的天堂，泰伯利亚人只需要死在死亡军团手下即可。战争还没开始就结束了，成千上万的人在暴君的身后丧生，被魔法束缚成为不死的奴仆。剩下的少数活着的战士分散在家园的残骸中，不知疲倦地寻找打败暴君的方法。领导大暴动，击败死亡军团，将这个可怕的霸主赶回大海深处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《暴君的祝福》是一款战术回合制游戏，你的规划、适应和战略能力比最大化你的部队或在宝库中找到最锋利的剑更重要。每天选择战斗，做出具有挑战性的选择，并巧妙地利用这些散兵叛乱分子的力量来击败不死部落，也许——只是也许——将真实的生命带回泰伯利亚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/7ddf694c06515b5c7a3eb2a8cce80701.avif?t=1771272977\" width=600 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/7862b98c947fdbb5b1df2a85cf1a0306.poster.avif?t=1771272977\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/7862b98c947fdbb5b1df2a85cf1a0306.webm?t=1771272977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/7862b98c947fdbb5b1df2a85cf1a0306.mp4?t=1771272977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在向暴君开战之前，你必须确保自己能够活到收复小岛的那天。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决定要战斗，从不死人手上拯救生者，还是积蓄力量。暴动每一天每个选择都至关重要。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你在泰伯利亚战场上奋战时，要面对一些难以抉择的随机事件。你是否要干预和打击强盗，置你的战士于险境？你是否要拯救一个孩子，冒着浪费宝贵时间和资源的风险？你的道德和信念会给你答案。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/deec89fdc20853093da4064e2857b855.avif?t=1771272977\" width=600 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/c911613a12a6332df094d67aaf404499.poster.avif?t=1771272977\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/c911613a12a6332df094d67aaf404499.webm?t=1771272977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/c911613a12a6332df094d67aaf404499.mp4?t=1771272977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>如果不摧毁一整个军团的不死人，就无法击败暴君。然而，获胜不仅仅是尽可能地重击敌人。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分析冲突做出相应规划。将战士放置在战场周围以获得战略优势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时刻注意周围环境：扬起灰尘使敌人看不见或跳过石头躲进灌木丛中以避免敌人的攻击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当心敌人：每次攻击都会发出信号，但要小心，移动会留下影子。如果没有办法避免的话，人物的影子仍然可以被攻击......</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将拦路的敌人撞到障碍物上，用可以抵御伤害的英雄保护较弱的英雄，以及利用环境进行强大的连锁元素攻击。蛮力有效，但智取更好，而非硬夺。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/cae99de49fb26a5b7dc07991ad9f3607.avif?t=1771272977\" width=600 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/95d569c28e7754b227e75e2060b4de0b.poster.avif?t=1771272977\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/95d569c28e7754b227e75e2060b4de0b.webm?t=1771272977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1520760/extras/95d569c28e7754b227e75e2060b4de0b.mp4?t=1771272977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你的每个英雄都有自己的个性、属性和能力。你要置谁于险境呢？</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募20位神圣的英雄，每个人都有一套独特的能力，可以极大地改变任何战斗的进程。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但注意：并不是所有的英雄都会出现在某周目中——也不是每个英雄都能保证完成任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为任务选择合适的团队。刺客在狭窄的空间里如鱼得水，而射手近距离则会很难受。一些英雄甚至会带着宠物，它们可能恰好能为团队赢得战斗。</p></li></ul>",
